text: Cartoon Network Russia and Southeastern Europe is a television channel broadcast in Bulgaria, Ukraine, Russia and the Balkans. It shows cartoons. The channel was created on 1 October 2009. It replaced the Pan-European Cartoon Network in those countries where this version is broadcast. It is available in three languages: Bulgarian, Russian and English. ==Programs== ===Current=== *Adventure Time (Финн и Джейк) *The Amazing World of Gumball *Apple & Onion *Aquaman: King of Atlantis *Be Cool, Scooby-Doo!
